<div><h3>SPAN 132 - Analyzing Stories and Poems </h3>  <p><hr>One of two &#8220;gateway&#8221; courses for the Spanish major and minor, this course introduces students to the analysis of literary texts in Spanish, as it explores the diverse cultural production of the Spanish-speaking world. May be taken before or after SPAN 131. Native speakers welcome.</p>

